                                    Countries needing urgent help
Identify top 10 countries needing urgent intervention 

Query
SELECT
  country_name,
  MAX(possible_cancer_cases)highest_cancer_cases,
  MIN(coverage) low_coverage
FROM cancer_data
GROUP BY country_name
ORDER BY highest_cancer_cases DESC
LIMIT 10;

Insight
There are some countries with high deaths and low coverage rate , which makes them at higher risk.

Recommendation
We should Focus resources and support on these countries first.
